Package: metro
Title: Washington Metropolitan Area Transit Authority API
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kiernan",
           family = "Nicholls",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kiernann@protonmail.com")
Description: The Washington Metropolitan Area Transit Authority
    is the government agency that operates the light rail and passenger
    buses of the Washington D.C. area. The WMATA provides a free API that
    can be used to access train arrivals, bus predictions, schedules, and
    more. This data is returned as tidy data frames for easy analysis. A
    free developer account and API key is needed.
License: GPL-3
